Hellooo, everyone....ohkay before I say anything 
Thankyou to each and every one in my insta family for wishing me and sending loads of love through your dm's and story shares.❤❤

And yes,, Sunday is back ! And it's my Birthday too , obviously I want to look good . Hence, checkout todays  #sundayskincareseries tutorial to have a glowing and bright skin for any occasion.🤩

I am using @niconi.beauty 's skin care set which is just amazing and very affordable in price . Yes , the facial set which I am using is just Rs. 250/- ! ! !😌

This kit consists of various products essentially made for moisturizing ones skin. 

Follow these steps, to get a ready look in less than 10 mins😄
Step 1.
 Cleansing cream, start by cleaning your face gently with niconi 's cleansing wash

Step 2.
Massage scrub, 
Scrub your face and massage it with the particular pack to remove the rough dirt and dead skin cells.

Step3.
Collagen gel , 
It is used to improve the fatty oils by in your skin and reduces wrinkles.

Step 4.
Face gel, gently use the gel on your face and make sure u cover all the parts. 

Step 5.
Wet face pack, which instantly moisturizes your skin to give a glowing look.

Step 6.
Face serum, for giving a last touch glow and helping in reduce the blemishes.

Now that was some serious skin care routine ,😂but u gotta do it anyway because you love your self.❤☺️
Ohkay fam! 
Until next sunday👋👋❤
